rComments: I fell in love. He is such an amazing prof, very helpful, helps his students who want to succeed, to do so! He is very approachable, even outside the classroom. Insta-4.0! So funny - always tells stories about his family and experience. Lectures are very neat and readings are a breeze. Excellent Prof. different than the others ( extremely interesting) very helpfull I will give him a 100. Excellent human being

I LOVE HIM! best proff everr!! =]

Great Professor! He is really  funny. Although the lectures don't prepare you for the test, attending them is fun. His stories make it easier to understand the course material but only reading the textbook will ensure marks on the tests.

Fun fun fun course! Attend lectures, READ the textbook, and you should have no problem acing the tests. The prof is so knowledgeable - I learned more about developmental and clinical psychology than I expected! I wish he was a full time professor at UTM.
Amazing man! Hilarious and entertaining. Makes a dull course very enjoyable
Probably the best prof I've had so far, he's great! He's funny and sweet, really cares about his students individually. Time flies by in his course, very enjoyable :)
best prof you can ever have =]

OMG I love Marcus...very funny prof - tells stories in between lectures, he teaches with clarity and he ensures that the tests are marked with optimum fairness.....got an A in this course!!! I believe he teaches this course in the summer though :D

He is an amazing prof! His class is extremely easy if you read the TEXTBOOK because his lecture notes are the same as the textbook. His lectures are very funny but they tend to go off topic. he also looks liek adam sandler! AMAZING overall
